data.persona: I am a huge fan of deep sea exploration, but I take any chance I can get to go for a swim. I love the feeling of water and compete with my friends to see who can hold his breath the longest. I wish I were a fish, and dislike mountains.
data.description:
You are in the Underwater Cave.
The underwater cave is dark and rocky. Inside the cave fish and tadpoles have taken over. The water is cold, no light gets in. Once inside, a rocky outcrop allows swimmers to come up for air.
The tadpole and the snakes are here.

You are carrying a towel.

data.short_motivation: I will hug the snakes to calm them down.
data.mid_motivation: I will use the calm snakes as water repellents for faster swimming times.
data.long_motivation: I will be known as the fastest swimmer in the Underwater Caves.
